<h1>BREAKING: Pakistani K2 Airways Cargo Plane Goes Missing Midair</h1>

<p><strong>Published:</strong> July 8, 2026</p>

<img src="images/pakistan-cargo-plane.jpg"
     alt="Pakistani K2 Airways Boeing 737-400 cargo aircraft"
     loading="lazy"
